<div class="full-width-layout__article-copy-section light">
	<div class="full-width-layout__copy"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI physics models play a central role in the approach. Trained on McLaren’s extensive computational fluid dynamics simulations and materials, the models deliver real-time predictions of manufacturing performance, including for carbon fiber structures used to build cars.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The collaboration between McLaren, Rescale and NVIDIA showcases how AI physics models, intelligent agents and accelerated computing are reshaping modern engineering practice.&nbsp;</span></p>
