	<div class="full-width-layout__copy"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After the keynote, take in </span><a href="/gtc/session-catalog/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">sessions</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and activities across downtown San Jose.&nbsp;</span></p>
